      "span_text": "Although a censor can deploy advanced censorship methods like DPI to scan the detailed content of packets, a user can encrypt and obfuscate packets to look like something that would be allowed by the DPI, such as HTTP or HTTPS packets, which are rarely blocked [CITATION_1] ."
